channel.description:
[center][IMG]http://i1098.photobucket.com/albums/g378/jerkinwhite/Renaissance%20F2p/renaissancef2pbanner.jpg[/img]
Hello, and welcome to Renaissance F2p. Please take a look around, and try to keep this thread bumped. We will update frequently to keep you informed.
[IMG]http://i1098.photobucket.com/albums/g378/jerkinwhite/Renaissance%20F2p/renaissancef2pinformation.jpg[/img]
Renaissance F2p is a F2P only server, meaning it will not have things like god swords, dragon weapons, ancient magicks, etc.
The base is Project Insanity, and I am using Sagi-X Evolution as the source and Moving-Pkz/Eudora World's client as the client.
(More coming later today)
[IMG]http://i1098.photobucket.com/albums/g378/jerkinwhite/Renaissance%20F2p/renaissancef2pgoalsandupdates.jpg[/img]
